## CSRD Content in This Module

The following data files contain CSRD content:

- `data/descriptors.json` - Character descriptors (103 entries)
- `data/types.json` - Character types (4 core types: Warrior, Adept, Explorer, Speaker)
- `data/foci.json` - Character foci (142 entries)

These data files were extracted from:
- **Source**: [Old Gus' Cypher System Reference Document (OG-CSRD)](https://callmepartario.github.io/og-csrd/)
- **Editor**: Old Gus (partario.flynn@gmail.com)
- **License**: Cypher System Open License

